org.matsim.contrib.noise.handler

Class NoiseTimeTracker

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.matsim.contrib.noise.handler.NoiseTimeTracker
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LinkEnterEventHandler, PersonEntersVehicleEventHandler, TransitDriverStartsEventHandler, MatsimExtensionPoint, EventHandler

    public class NoiseTimeTracker
extends Object
implements PersonEntersVehicleEventHandler, LinkEnterEventHandler, TransitDriverStartsEventHandler
    A handler which computes noise emissions, immisions, affected agent units and damages for each receiver point and time interval. Throws noise damage events for each affected and causing agent.
    Author:
    ikaddoura
